'''2014年俄罗斯金融危机'''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-12-16/russian-government-to-meet-on-financial-chaos-as-ruble-dives-15-.html|title=Russian Government to Meet on Financial Chaos as Ruble Dives 15%|author=Ekaterina Shatalova|date=16 December 2014|accessdate=16 December 2014|work=Bloomberg|archive-date=2014-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141217064531/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-12-16/russian-government-to-meet-on-financial-chaos-as-ruble-dives-15-.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.haaretz.com/business/.premium-1.632266|title=Russian financial crisis’ effect on Israel to escalate|author=Ami Ginsburg|date=17 December 2014|accessdate=17 December 2014|work=Haaretz|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924044745/http://www.haaretz.com/business/.premium-1.632266|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="financialcrisis"/>是有关[[俄罗斯卢布|俄罗斯卢布]]及其他有关货币，货币的极速贬值与[[俄罗斯经济|俄罗斯经济]]增长放缓的事件<ref name="financialcrisis">{{cite web|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/yield-seekers-prone-to-russias-disease-heard-on-the-street-1418767459|title=Yield Seekers Prone to Russia’s Disease|author=Justin Lahart|date=16 December 2014|accessdate=16 December 2014|work=Wall Street Journal|archive-date=2020-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200907060556/https://www.wsj.com/articles/yield-seekers-prone-to-russias-disease-heard-on-the-street-1418767459|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="sanctions"/>。此次经济衰退一个重要因素与[[原油|原油]]有关，这是俄罗斯一大重要[[出口|出口]]品，其价格在2014年6月到12月16日期间几乎下降了一半<ref name="financialcrisis"/><ref name="oilpricedecline">{{cite web|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/oil-prices-plunge-with-brent-crude-below-60-1418722523|title=U.S. Oil Prices Snap Losing Streak|author=Nicole Friedman|accessdate=16 December 2014|date=16 December 2014|work=Wall Street Journal|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125032350/https://www.wsj.com/articles/oil-prices-plunge-with-brent-crude-below-60-1418722523|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

此次事件打击了俄罗斯经济，生产者和消费者皆受到损害，也使得俄罗斯的国际贸易受到消极影响。俄罗斯股市也受到了巨大的影响，[[RTS指數|俄罗斯指数]]从2014年12月初至12月16日已下跌了三成<ref name="russianstocks"/>。

