===油价下跌===
石油价格由2014年6月的每桶100美元下跌至2014年12月的每桶60美元<ref name=FChang>{{cite news|last1=Chung|first1=Frank|title=The Cold War is back, and colder|url=http://www.news.com.au/finance/economy/the-cold-war-is-back-and-colder/story-e6frflo9-1227159436375|accessdate=17 December 2014|publisher=News.au|date=18 December 2014|archive-date=2015-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150814142811/http://www.news.com.au/finance/economy/the-cold-war-is-back-and-colder/story-e6frflo9-1227159436375|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其原因主要是全球范围内对石油需求的减少，以及[[美国|美国]]頁岩油产量的增加<ref name=CMooney>{{cite news|last1=Mooney|first1=Chris|title=The basic reason oil keeps getting cheaper and cheaper|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/wonkblog/wp/2014/12/12/the-basic-reason-oil-keeps-getting-cheaper-and-cheaper/|accessdate=17 December 2014|publisher=Washington Post|date=12 December 2014|archive-date=2015-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150629202844/http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/wonkblog/wp/2014/12/12/the-basic-reason-oil-keeps-getting-cheaper-and-cheaper/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，由于俄罗斯联邦政府收入的近一半来自油气销售，价格下跌对俄国的打击严重<ref name=FChang/>；俄罗斯的经济可以说是受到“[[荷兰病|荷兰病]]”的困扰，即一国注重发展其自然资源而对其他经济活动造成损害<ref name=FCoppola>{{cite news|last1=Coppola|first1=Frances|title=Oil, Sanctions And Russian Politics|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/francescoppola/2014/12/01/oil-sanctions-and-russian-politics/|accessdate=17 December 2014|publisher=Forbes|date=1 December 2014|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112010446/https://www.forbes.com/sites/francescoppola/2014/12/01/oil-sanctions-and-russian-politics/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年，俄罗斯需要保持每桶100美元的油价才能维持预算平衡<ref name=LElliott>{{cite news|last1=Elliott|first1=Larry|title=Fears for Russian rouble as plunging oil price dents markets|url=http://www.theguardian.com/business/2014/dec/15/fears-russian-rouble-oil-price-markets|accessdate=17 December 2014|publisher=The Guardian|date=15 December 2014|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112034255/http://www.theguardian.com/business/2014/dec/15/fears-russian-rouble-oil-price-markets|dead-url=no}}</ref>。俄罗斯并不是唯一一个受到油价下跌影响的国家；其他一些国家，例如[[委内瑞拉|委内瑞拉]]、[[尼日利亚|尼日利亚]]和[[哈萨克斯坦|哈萨克斯坦]]同样受到了收入下降和经济活动衰退的影响<ref name=Ticking>{{cite news|last1=Schoen|first1=John|title=Ticking time bombs: Where oil's fall is dangerous|url=http://www.cnbc.com/id/102270286#.|accessdate=17 December 2014|publisher=CNBC|date=16 December 2014|archive-date=2015-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150203043825/http://www.cnbc.com/id/102270286#.|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 经济制裁 ===
2014年俄罗斯对乌克兰的军事干预使任何对于俄罗斯的国际援助希望渺茫<ref name="financialcrisis"/>。美国[[白宫|白宫]]官员同时指出，尽管发生了经济危机，[[美国|美国]]与[[欧盟|欧盟]]因俄罗斯先前[[吞并克里米亚|吞并克里米亚]]并在[[顿巴斯战争|顿巴斯战争]]中援助了反乌的[[新俄罗斯|新俄罗斯]]武装分子，将不会缓解{{link-en|针对俄罗斯的经济制裁|International sanctions during the 2014 pro-Russian unrest in Ukraine}}<ref name="sanctions">{{cite web|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-12-16/u-s-won-t-ease-sanctions-to-prevent-economic-meltdown-in-russia.html|title=U.S. Won’t Ease Sanctions to Stem Russia’s Economic Crisis|author=Mike Dorning and Ian Katz|date=16 December 2014|accessdate=16 December 2014|work=Bloomberg|archive-date=2014-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141217064620/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-12-16/u-s-won-t-ease-sanctions-to-prevent-economic-meltdown-in-russia.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美国认为经济制裁已对当前俄经济造成负面影响，并且预期此次经济制裁将使俄经济发生更大幅度的衰退<ref name="sanctions"/>。

自从俄公司被禁止滚动融资, 并被强制在公开市场上将卢布兑换成美元或者其他外国货币以满足他们对于已有债务的利息支付义务，此次经济制裁也引起了卢布贬值<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/russian-companies-clamor-for-dollars-to-repay-debt-1412860551|title=Russian Companies Clamor for Dollars to Repay Debt|author=Chiara Albanese and Ben Edwards|date=9 October 2014|accessdate=16 December 2014|work=Wall Street Journal|archive-date=2020-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200907060603/https://www.wsj.com/articles/russian-companies-clamor-for-dollars-to-repay-debt-1412860551|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

