t.com/blogs/wonkblog/wp/2014/12/16/checkmate-putin-russias-economy-is-stuck-in-a-catch-22/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外，普京控诉西方国家一手策划了俄罗斯经济危机的爆发<ref name="Armen">{{cite journal |first=Armen |last=Grigoryan |date=11 December 2014 |url=http://www.jamestown.org/single/?tx_ttnews%5Btt_news%5D=43192&tx_ttnews%5BbackPid%5D=7#.VJH-WId0y71 |title=Russian-Abkhazian Strategic Partnership Agreement Puts Pressure on Armenian Government |volume=Volume 11 |issue=221 |work=Eurasia Daily Monitor |publisher=The Jamestown Foundation |accessdate=17 December 2014 |journal= |archive-date=2016-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160317050647/http://www.jamestown.org/single/?tx_ttnews%5Btt_news%5D=43192&tx_ttnews%5BbackPid%5D=7#.VJH-WId0y71 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://dw.de/p/1Dz7V |title=Putin blames West for Ukraine 'tragedy' |date=4 December 2014 |publisher=[[Deutsche_Welle|Deutsche Welle]] |accessdate=17 December 2014 |archive-date=2019-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912020741/https://www.dw.com/en/putin-blames-west-for-ukraine-tragedy/a-18109549 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 俄罗斯货币政策 ==
=== 俄罗斯卢布的贬值 ===
[[经济大衰退|2007年经济大衰退]]以来，由于各国[[央行|央行]]非常规的刺激性操作，[[美国国债|美国国债]]和其他低风险资产的收益率明显下降，这些刺激性操作包括“[[零利率政策|零利率政策]]”（ZIRP）和[[量化宽松|量化宽松]]等。如此一来，出于收益最大化的考虑，[[发达国家|发达国家]]的投资者为使其持有资产有更高利率，不断购买[[新兴市场|新兴市场]]的债务。这造成了俄罗斯企业发行的以外币计价的债务规模不断上升，截至2014年6月，外币计价的债务规模已达到5020亿，而2007年底仅有3250亿<ref name="financialcrisis"/>。

由于卢布最近贬值，俄罗斯企业应当支付的债务利息成本明显上升。因为这些债务是以美元或者其他相对卢布升值的货币发行的，俄罗斯企业需要花费更多的以卢布计价的收入才能偿付那些美元或其他外币的债权人<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/11/10/russia-rouble-debt-idUSL6N0T02OR20141110|title=Falling rouble creates debt payment headache for Russian companies|author=Sujata Rao|date=10 November 2014|accessdate=16 December 2014|work=Reuters|archive-date=2015-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002080637/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/11/10/russia-rouble-debt-idUSL6N0T02OR20141110|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 中央银行的介入 ===
2014年12月15日，俄罗斯的外汇储备为近4000亿美元，为[[各国外汇储备列表|世界第六高]]<ref name=FWeir>{{cite news|last1=Weir|first1=Fred|title=Oil prices, ruble, inflation all bite Russia, but how badly?|url=http://www.csmonitor.com/World/Europe/2014/1215/Oil-prices-ruble-inflation-all-bite-Russia-but-how-badly-video|accessdate=17 December 2014|publisher=Christian Science Monitor|date=15 December 2014|archive-date=2016-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161223044643/http://www.csmonitor.com/World/Europe/2014/1215/Oil-prices-ruble-inflation-all-bite-Russia-but-how-badly-video|dead-url=no}}</ref>。外汇储备使俄国有能力抬升卢布价值<ref name=FWeir/>。12月15日，俄罗斯央行花费近20亿美元，试图稳定卢布<ref name="afptweet">{{cite web|title=#BREAKING: Russia's central bank spent almost $2 bn to support ruble on Monday|url=https://twitter.com/AFP/status/545117472911654912|date=17 December 2014|accessdate=17 December 2014|work=Agence-France Presse|publisher=Twitter|archive-date=2020-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200719064000/https://twitter.com/AFP/status/545117472911654912|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[莫斯科时间|当地时间]]2014年12月16日凌晨1时不到，俄罗斯央行将其基准利率由10.5%提升至17%，试图缓解或阻止卢布继续贬值<ref name="interestratesbloomberg">{{cite web|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-12-15/russia-increases-key-interest-rate-to-17-to-stem-ruble-decline.html|title=Russia Defends Ruble With Biggest Rate Rise Since 1998|author=Olga Tanas and Anna Andrianova|date=16 December 2014|accessdate=16 December 2014|work=Bloomberg|archive-date=2015-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150127080441/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-12-15/russia-increases-key-interest-rate-to-17-to-stem-ruble-decline.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="washingtonpost">{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/to-halt-crisis-russia-central-bank-hikes-interest-rates-as-ruble-falls/2014/12/16/9ebb1610-4c9e-45bd-9297-475b0d3878cc_story.html|title=Russia imposes steep interest rate hike as ruble plummets|author=Michael Birnbaum|date=16 December 2014|accessdate=16 December 2014|work=Washington Post|archive-date=2020-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024184639/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/to-halt-crisis-russia-central-bank-hikes-interest-rates-as-ruble-falls/2014/12/16/9ebb1610-4c9e-45bd-9297-475b0d3878cc_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这是2014年俄罗斯央行的第六次加息操作<ref name="interestratesbloomberg"/>。

虽然央行在凌晨进行干预，卢布仍然继续贬值。2014年12月16日早晨，美元兑卢布汇率一度达到79，而2014年1月这一汇率为33<ref name="washingtonpost"/>。16日俄罗斯央行宣布其不会加强[[资本管制|资本管制]]，卢布维持在了低位<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nasdaq.com/article/midday-update-stocks-reverse-course-as-oil-stocks-offer-buying-opportunity-ruble-recovers-cm423871|title=Midday Update: Stocks Reverse Course as Oil Stocks Offer Buying Opportunity, Ruble Recovers|author=MT Newswires|date=16 December 2014|accessdate=16 December 2014|work=NASDAQ|archive-date=2018-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180919141252/https://www.nasdaq.com/article/midday-update-stocks-reverse-course-as-oil-stocks-offer-buying-opportunity-ruble-recovers-cm423871|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

12月22日，俄罗斯央行向莫斯科信托银行提供5.3亿美元貸款，这也是金融危机中第一家接受政府救济的银行<ref name=LElliott2>{{cite news|last1=Elliott|first1=Larry|title=IMF raises fears of global crisis as Russian bank forced into bailout|url=http://www.theguardian.com/business/2014/dec/22/trust-bank-first-financial-casualty-russia-currency-crisis|accessdate=23 December 2014|publisher=The Guardian|date=22 December 2014|archive-date=2020-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806191037/https://www.theguardian.com/business/2014/dec/22/trust-bank-first-financial-casualty-russia-currency-crisis|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

